      "lk_opt_5": "4 - Almost Always",
      "instructions_221301": "Please respond to each question or statement by marking one button.Physical Function Mobility:",
      "pediatric_qol_physicalfunction_exercise": "In the past 7 days I could do sports and exercise that other kids my age could do",
      "pediatric_qol_physicalfunction_exercise_opt_1": "4 - With no trouble",
